27:05.406 --> 27:07.060
BOY,
DID I HAVE YOU PEGGED WRONG.

27:07.669 --> 27:11.630
YOU ARE THE MOST INSENSITIVE,

27:11.760 --> 27:14.502
-THE CRUELEST--
-OH GO TO SLEEP, WILL YOU?

27:14.633 --> 27:15.546
HEARTLESS...

27:15.677 --> 27:18.071
WILL YOU JUST GO NIGHT-NIGHT?

27:18.985 --> 27:20.551
GIVE ME THE BLANKET.

27:20.682 --> 27:22.292
NO WAY.

27:22.423 --> 27:23.816
GIVE ME THE BLANKET.

27:24.555 --> 27:25.426
IT'S NOT GONNA HAPPEN.

27:29.778 --> 27:31.258
GIVE ME THE BLANKET.

27:33.521 --> 27:34.653
ALL RIGHT, RYKER.

27:34.783 --> 27:36.002
IT WILL BE A COLD DAY IN CUBA

27:36.132 --> 27:37.481
BEFORE YOU GET THIS BLANKET,
YOU GOT THAT?

27:37.612 --> 27:39.179
-OH, REALLY?
-YEAH, REALLY.

27:40.136 --> 27:41.485
WE'LL SEE ABOUT THAT.

27:41.616 --> 27:45.664
[OVERLAPPING ARGUING]

27:47.056 --> 27:48.318
STOP IT, THAT'S NOT FUNNY!

27:50.407 --> 27:51.931
[HEAD SLAMMING]

27:52.061 --> 27:52.888
OH, GOD.

27:53.019 --> 27:54.324
[ALEX GROANING PAINFULLY]

27:56.413 --> 27:57.284
I HEARD THAT.

27:58.372 --> 27:59.286
GOD!

27:59.416 --> 28:00.504
[GROANING]

28:00.635 --> 28:01.636
YOU OK?

28:03.159 --> 28:05.509
UH, YEAH.

28:07.381 --> 28:08.251
THANKS.

28:11.211 --> 28:12.081
WELCOME.

28:56.212 --> 29:00.564
UH, MORNING, NEWMIE.

