[CAMERA CLICKING]

29:16.319 --> 29:17.538
YOU KNOW WHAT?

29:17.668 --> 29:21.150
OPEN UP TO GET SOME RIGHT HERE,
BELOW THEIR...

29:21.281 --> 29:23.500
YOU'RE NOT LOOKING, RIGHT HERE.

29:23.631 --> 29:24.458
FINE, IT'S FINE.

29:24.588 --> 29:25.633
BUT I DON'T WANT FULL LENGTH.

29:26.329 --> 29:27.200
HEY!

29:27.722 --> 29:28.941
HEY.

29:29.071 --> 29:29.985
